  "caption": "The track opens with a series of deep, cinematic cinematic impacts each punctifying a space soundscape. A delicate, crystalline music box melody enters, creating a stark, eerie contrast with the futuristic atmosphere. A clear, almost childlike female vocal begins singing in French, her delivery precise and slightly robotic, enhanced by a spacious reverb. The arrangement gradually builds, introducing a steady, driving drum machine beat and a subtle synth bassline. The chorus elevates the energy with layered, harmonized vocals and a more powerful delivery, creating a sense of grand, synthetic drama. The song progresses through dynamic shifts, including a more intense bridge and a powerful final chorus, before deconstructing into a sparse outro where the music box melody and atmospheric sounds fade into silence.",
